---
const features = [
  '10–20 enhanced existing photos',
  'Cover photo recommendation',
  'Optimized photo order',
  'Three title options',
  'Rewritten Airbnb-ready description',
  'Photo captions guests actually read',
  '30-second vertical reel from existing assets',
  'Mini competitor and pricing note',
  'Top 10 action list',
  'Paste-ready delivery file'
];
---
<div class="offer-card">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">Core package</p>
    <h2>Full Listing Glow-Up</h2>
    <div class="price">$300</div>
    <p class="price-anchor">One-time, no subscription. If it wins you a single extra booking, it’s already paid for itself.</p>
    <p>This is my done-for-you listing presentation upgrade. I built it for hosts whose property is better than their current photos, title, and story suggest — and I do every one by hand.</p>
    <p class="capacity-note"><span class="capacity-dot"></span>I take a limited number of listings each week so I can review each one properly.</p>
    <a class="button primary" href="/score/">Start with my free listing score</a>
    <p class="offer-microcopy">I’ll send you a real preview before you ever pay.</p>
  </div>
  <ul class="feature-list">
    {features.map((feature) => <li>{feature}</li>)}
  </ul>
</div>
